A highly detailed, cinematic painting of a gleaming, ornate chalice overflowing with viscous, iridescent black liquid. A shadowy, robed figure – a pimp-like figure – stands dramatically in the foreground, holding the chalice aloft, casting a sinister glow. The background is a swirling, chaotic void filled with fractured, ethereal landscapes. Dramatic lighting, dark fantasy, Magic: The Gathering art.